<div class="card">
  <h5 class="card-header">Button</h5>
  <div class="card-body">
    <h5 class="card-title">All settings will be changed back to default</h5>
    <p class="card-text">Once clicked, will brings settings back to default. How can the settings be saved?</p>
    <%= button_to 'Button', root_path, class: 'btn btn-primary', method: :get %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h5 class="card-header">Link</h5>
  <div class="card-body">
    <h5 class="card-title">Loading class does not get removed and does the opposite stylesheet</h5>
    <p class="card-text">Once clicked, it will change the stylesheet to the opposite stylesheet and then the body
      loading class will not be removed. If Light Mode, then will change the background to Dark and vice versa</p>
    <p class="card-text">If the class is manually removed via Inspect Element, the elements on the page are no longer
      hidden, the icons disappear in the left sidebar, topbar turns dark, unable to condense the second menu, and cannot
      change settings.</p>
    <p class="card-text">Any help will be greatly appreciated.</p>
    <%= link_to 'Root URL ', root_url %> | <%= link_to 'Root Path', root_path, class: 'reload' %> |
    <%= link_to (image_pack_tag 'media/images/logo-sm.png', alt: '', height: 28), root_path, class: 'logo' %>

  </div>
</div>


<div class="card">
  <h5 class="card-header">Testing javascript</h5>
  <div class="card-body">
    <h5 class="card-title">Only used for testing</h5>
    <!-- Button trigger modal -->
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#exampleModal">
      Launch demo modal
    </button>

    <!-- Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Modal title</h5>
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
              <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
            ...
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Save changes</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Tooltip on top">
      Tooltip on top
    </button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="right" title="Tooltip on right">
      Tooltip on right
    </button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" title="Tooltip on bottom">
      Tooltip on bottom
    </button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="left" title="Tooltip on left">
      Tooltip on left
    </button>

    <button type="button" class="btn btn-lg btn-danger" data-toggle="popover" title="Popover title" data-content="And here's some amazing content. It's very engaging. Right?">Click
      to toggle popover
    </button>
  </div>
</div>
